# TwinMind does NOT read a Groq key from server env by design.
# Each user pastes their own key in the Settings modal; it lives in their
# browser's localStorage and is sent per-request via the x-groq-key header
# to /api/transcribe (and, in Phase 2, /api/suggest and /api/chat).
#
# This file exists as documentation only. There are no required env vars.
